    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine has had an initial 10 min, add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>red onion wedges</strong> and<strong> crushed garlic </strong>to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and<strong> yellow mustard seeds</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together</p>",
