    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Squeeze half the<strong> lemon wedges</strong> over the <strong>potatoes</strong> and add the squeezed wedges to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> (save the remaining wedges for garnish)</p><p>Add in the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>curry marinade </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 30 min or until everything is cooked through and tender</p>",
      "order": 6,
