    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's cooked through and tender, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and top everything with the<strong> spinach </strong>then return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 5 min or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Meanwhile, slice the<strong> red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Once the spinach has wilted, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>from the oven<strong> </strong>and stir the it through the potatoes and onion wedges – this is your <strong>Indian-style spiced aubergine tray bake with spinach</strong></p>",
