      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indian-style spiced aubergine </strong>with the <strong>potato</strong>,<strong> spinach </strong>and<strong> onion wedges </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>nigella seeds</strong> and <strong>lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
